entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You helped Radeld out with some problems he was having on Naboo.
entries.journal_entry_description: Radeld has some things he needs taken care of on Naboo, and you're the best person for the job.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: You did good work for me on Tatooine. Now do some more. Skaak's are cutting into my business. Deal with them.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Radeld wants you to take care of some Skaak Tippers. They're cutting into his business somehow, and he wants to send them a message.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: The only thing worse than Skaak's is Maulers. They've got the RSF riled up on Naboo and I can't move spices. Quiet them down, would you?
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Radeld wants you to deal with some Maulers. They're making it hard for his people to move spices on Naboo.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: I'll say it again, you do excellent work. You're well on your way to earning the title of Master Smuggler. Maybe we'll talk again someday...
